  "body": "Identified in this comment: https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/issues/1017#issuecomment-447559851\r\n\r\nWe should visibly fail when two processes attempt to access the datadir concurrently. \r\nThe database package should maintain a lock of some kind and throw a fatal error if attempting to access a datadir which is already locked by another process.\r\n\r\n",
